<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Books Project</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/index.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/component.css">
</head>
<body>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">

    <div class="book-badge">
      <div class="card back"></div>
      <div class="card front">
        <span><%=totalBooks  %></span>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="intro">
        Hey, my name is  <strong>Clematins</strong>, & these are <mark>books</mark> I've read...
      </p>

      <p class="hint">
        You can Sort by the most recent, rating, title, or best
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/books/new" class="btn primary">Add Book</a>
      <div class="sort">
        <p>Sort by</p>
       <span class="sort-type">
      <a href="?sort=recent">Recent</a>
          <a href="?sort=rating">Rating</a>
          <a href="?sort=title">Title</a>
    </span>
       </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</header>

<main class="container">